channel.title: Problem with mopar
channel.description:
Hey I used to play private servers alot but then got back into rs staking. But I've got back into them again ;) One problem though, everytime I try to run a server it goes into a black screen and tells me;
Sorry an error has occured whilst loading runescape to fix this try in the following order
1: close all open web browsers and reloading 2: Try clearing your web browsers cache 3: Try using a different game world 4: Try reebooting your computer 5: Try selecting a different version of java.
K, but i've tried all servers haha, well atleast 20. And I have the latest version of java.. What could be wrong ;[
